reviews.review_text: Really appreciate how clean it is inside. All tables had just been wiped when I walked in making me comfortable to sit in. The floors were just moped aswell and the condiment stand and garbage clear. My meal was also great. Really hot fries and warm burger. I got the crispy chicken deluxe meal. The till person at the front was nice, had a smile and a good attitude. I appreciate all these things amounting to a great visit!
